data.description: Seller offering $10k towards closing costs! Discover your ideal home in this charming three-bedroom, one-bathroom rambler. Recently updated, it boasts a new roof, freshly painted interiors and exteriors, a cleaned-out crawl space with new insulation, a new water heater, and a fully remodeled bathroom. A versatile carport that accommodates cars or an RV. This property offers a serene and comfortable environment that's ready for you to make it your own. Close to the 522 and Woodinvile.
